# Billing

<% if @stripe_customer&.active? %>
## Status

**Active** — [Manage payment](/billing/portal)

## Your Subscription

| Item | Cost |
|------|------|
| <%= @current_user.display_name %> (you) | <%= @current_user.counts_self_for_paid_human_features? ? "$3/mo (programmatic access)" : "$0/mo" %> |
<% @active_agents&.each do |agent| %>
| <%= agent.display_name %> (agent) | <%= agent.billing_exempt? ? "$0/mo (exempt)" : "$3/mo" %> |
<% end %>
<% @active_collectives&.each do |collective| %>
| <%= collective.name %> (collective) | <%= collective.billing_exempt? ? "$0/mo (exempt)" : "$3/mo" %> |
<% end %>
| **Total** | **$<%= (@billable_quantity || 0) * 3 %>/mo** |

<% if @lapsed_collectives&.any? %>
## Billing Lapsed

Paid features on these collectives are paused. Restore your subscription at `/billing` to resume — your configuration is preserved.

| Collective | Status |
|------------|--------|
<% @lapsed_collectives.each do |collective| %>
| <%= collective.name %> | features paused — $3/mo when restored |
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if @pending_agents&.any? || @pending_collectives&.any? %>
## Pending Resources

These resources will activate once billing is set up.

| Item | Status |
|------|--------|
<% @pending_agents&.each do |agent| %>
| <%= agent.display_name %> (agent) | pending — $3/mo when active |
<% end %>
<% @pending_collectives&.each do |collective| %>
| <%= collective.name %> (collective) | pending — $3/mo when active |
<% end %>
<% end %>

<% if @inactive_agents&.any? || @inactive_collectives&.any? %>
## Inactive Resources

These resources are deactivated and not being billed.

| Item | Status |
|------|--------|
<% @inactive_agents&.each do |agent| %>
| <%= agent.display_name %> (agent) | not billed |
<% end %>
<% @inactive_collectives&.each do |collective| %>
| <%= collective.name %> (collective) | not billed |
<% end %>
<% end %>

To deactivate or reactivate resources, visit `/billing` in your browser.

## AI Agent Credits

<% if @credit_balance_cents.nil? %>
Balance unavailable — try refreshing.
<% else %>
**Balance: $<%= format("%.2f", @credit_balance_cents / 100.0) %>**
<% if @credit_balance_cents == 0 %>

Add funds to run AI agents.
<% end %>
<% end %>

To add credits, visit `/billing` in your browser and use the "Add Funds" button.
